---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="소개 & 문의 — Rabbit Logs"
  description="코드는 몰라도, 프로세스는 가장 잘 아는 사람. SAP를 '사용하는' 현업 실무자의 눈으로 일의 흐름을 기록하는 공간입니다."
  lang="ko"
>
  <article class="prose page about">
    <div class="about-hero">
      <img src="/images/hero-rabbit.png" alt="Rabbit Logs 토끼 캐릭터" class="about-logo" />
      <h1>코드는 몰라도,<br />프로세스는 잘 아는 사람</h1>
    </div>

    <p class="lead">생산 PI와 SAP PP 구축, 안정화 프로젝트를 거쳐,<br />지금도 SAP를 <strong>'사용하는' 현업 실무자</strong>로 일하고 있습니다.</p>

    <p class="lead">일하면서 배운 것을, 일하는 사람의 언어로 기록합니다.<br />그리고 데이터로 시야를 넓혀가는 과정도 함께 남깁니다.</p>

    <ul class="timeline">
      <li><div class="tl-body">
        <p class="tl-title">생산 PI</p>
        <p class="tl-desc">현장 프로세스 분석·개선</p>
      </div></li>
      <li><div class="tl-body">
        <p class="tl-title">SAP PP 구축</p>
        <p class="tl-desc">To-Be 설계·개발·테스트</p>
      </div></li>
      <li><div class="tl-body">
        <p class="tl-title">SAP PP 안정화</p>
        <p class="tl-desc">Go-Live 이후 이슈 대응</p>
      </div></li>
      <li><div class="tl-body">
        <p class="tl-title">SAP PP 보완</p>
        <p class="tl-desc">운영 중 개선·추가 개발</p>
      </div></li>
      <li><div class="tl-body">
        <p class="tl-title">現 현업 실무자</p>
        <p class="tl-desc">SAP를 쓰는 쪽에서 기록</p>
      </div></li>
    </ul>

    <div class="motto">
      <p class="motto-main">기능보다 프로세스, 화면보다 사람.</p>
      <p class="motto-sub">T-code 목록보다, 그 화면을 왜 그렇게 쓰는지를 씁니다.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section-label"><h2>무엇을 기록하나요</h2></div>
    <div class="cat-grid">
      <a href="/category/project" class="cat-card cat-project">
        <p class="cat-name">SAP 프로젝트</p>
        <p class="cat-desc">구축 현장의 판단과 시행착오</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/category/operations" class="cat-card cat-operations">
        <p class="cat-name">SAP 실무운영</p>
        <p class="cat-desc">화면 뒤에서 벌어지는 일</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/category/study" class="cat-card cat-study">
        <p class="cat-name">SAP 학습자료</p>
        <p class="cat-desc">처음 배우는 눈높이의 개념 정리</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/category/stats" class="cat-card cat-stats">
        <p class="cat-name">통계·데이터</p>
        <p class="cat-desc">숫자로 업무를 다시 보는 연습</p>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="section-label"><h2>문의</h2></div>
    <div class="cta-row">
      <a href="mailto:contact@rabbitlogs.com" class="cta-card">
        <span class="cta-label">MAIL</span>
        <span class="cta-text">
          <span class="cta-value">contact@rabbitlogs.com</span>
          <span class="cta-hint">나누고 싶은 이야기가 있다면</span>
        </span>
      </a>
      <a href="/rss.xml" class="cta-card">
        <span class="cta-label">RSS</span>
        <span class="cta-text">
          <span class="cta-value">새 글 구독하기</span>
          <span class="cta-hint">알림 없이, 읽고 싶을 때만</span>
        </span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </article>

  <style>
    .about { max-width: 640px; }

    /* ── 히어로 ── */
    .about-hero {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 0 0 1.6rem;
      padding: 1.8rem 1rem 1.4rem;
      position: relative;
    }
    .about-hero::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 60% at 50% 35%, rgba(44,95,87,0.07) 0%, rgba(44,95,87,0) 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .about-logo { width: 118px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto 0.9rem; display: block; position: relative; }
    .about-hero h1 { font-weight: 800; font-size: 2rem; letter-spacing: -0.03em; margin: 0; line-height: 1.35; position: relative; }

    .about .lead { font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; color: var(--ink); margin: 0.9rem 0; text-align: center; }
    .about .lead strong { color: var(--primary); font-weight: 700; }

    /* ── 섹션 라벨 ── */
    .section-label {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.7rem;
      margin: 2.2rem 0 0.9rem;
    }
    .about .section-label h2 {
      font-size: 1.08rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 0;
      white-space: nowrap; letter-spacing: -0.01em; text-align: left;
    }
    .about .section-label h2::before { content: none; }
    .section-label::after { content: ''; flex: 1; height: 1px; background: var(--line); }

    /* ── 가로 타임라인 (점 위아래 교차) ── */
    .timeline {
      list-style: none; padding: 0 9%; margin: 2.8rem 0; position: relative;
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
      min-height: 150px; align-items: center;
    }
    .timeline::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; left: 9%; right: 9%; top: 50%;
      transform: translateY(-50%); height: 2px;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(44,95,87,0.22), var(--primary));
    }
    .timeline li {
      position: relative; padding: 0; margin: 0; text-align: center; height: 100%;
    }
    .tl-body {
      position: absolute; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 155px; bottom: calc(50% + 34px);
    }
    .timeline li:nth-child(even) .tl-body {
      bottom: auto; top: calc(50% + 34px);
    }
    .timeline li::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; left: 50%; top: 50%;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
      width: 12px; height: 12px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--paper); border: 2.5px solid rgba(44,95,87,0.5);
      z-index: 1;
    }
    .timeline li::after {
      content: ''; position: absolute; left: 50%; width: 1px;
      background: rgba(44,95,87,0.28);
      top: calc(50% - 28px); height: 22px;
    }
    .timeline li:nth-child(even)::after { top: auto; bottom: calc(50% - 28px); }
    .timeline li:last-child::before {
      background: var(--primary); border-color: var(--primary);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(44,95,87,0.14);
    }
    .tl-title { font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.95rem; margin: 0; color: var(--ink); letter-spacing: -0.02em; line-height: 1.35; white-space: nowrap; }
    .timeline li:last-child .tl-title { color: var(--primary); }
    .tl-desc { font-size: 0.79rem; color: var(--muted); margin: 0.18rem 0 0; line-height: 1.4; white-space: nowrap; }

    /* ── 모토 ── */
    .motto {
      text-align: center; margin: 3rem 0; padding: 0 1rem;
    }
    .motto::before,
    .motto::after {
      content: ''; display: block; width: 32px; height: 2px;
      background: var(--primary); opacity: 0.5; margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .motto::before { margin-bottom: 1.4rem; }
    .motto::after { margin-top: 1.4rem; }
    .motto-main {
      font-size: 1.32rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--primary);
      line-height: 1.5; margin: 0; letter-spacing: -0.02em; word-break: keep-all;
    }
    .motto-sub {
      font-size: 0.92rem; color: var(--muted); margin: 0.65rem 0 0;
      line-height: 1.65; word-break: keep-all;
    }

    /* ── 카테고리 카드 ── */
    .cat-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 0.7rem; margin: 0; }
    .cat-card {
      display: block; text-decoration: none; color: inherit;
      background: var(--tk-bg); border: 1px solid var(--tk-border);
      border-left: 3px solid var(--tk-line);
      border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0; padding: 0.7rem 0.85rem;
      transition: transform 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease;
    }
    .cat-card:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(32,37,31,0.08); }
    .cat-name { font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--tk-fg); margin: 0 0 0.12rem; line-height: 1.35; }
    .cat-desc { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--muted); margin: 0; line-height: 1.45; word-break: keep-all; }
    .cat-project   { --tk-bg: #eef4f2; --tk-line: #2c5f57; --tk-fg: #234b45; --tk-border: #cfe3de; }
    .cat-operations{ --tk-bg: #eef2f7; --tk-line: #3b6ea5; --tk-fg: #2f5885; --tk-border: #cddced; }
    .cat-study     { --tk-bg: #fbf3e6; --tk-line: #d99441; --tk-fg: #a8701f; --tk-border: #f0dbb3; }
    .cat-stats     { --tk-bg: #f7eef1; --tk-line: #a8516e; --tk-fg: #8a4159; --tk-border: #eccfd9; }

    /* ── 문의 + 구독 CTA ── */
    .cta-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 0.7rem; margin: 0; }
    .cta-card {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.7rem;
      text-decoration: none; color: inherit;
      background: var(--color-bg-soft); border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 8px; padding: 0.65rem 0.85rem; text-align: left;
      transition: border-color 0.15s ease, background 0.15s ease;
    }
    .cta-card:hover { border-color: var(--primary); background: #eef4f2; }
    .cta-label {
      flex-shrink: 0; font-size: 0.66rem; font-weight: 700; color: #fff;
      background: var(--primary); padding: 0.2rem 0.45rem; border-radius: 5px;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }
    .cta-text { min-width: 0; }
    .cta-value {
      display: block; font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--primary);
      line-height: 1.35; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .cta-hint { display: block; font-size: 0.73rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.4; }

    /* ── 모바일: 타임라인 세로 전환 ── */
    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .about-hero h1 { font-size: 1.75rem; }
      .about-logo { width: 115px; }
      .cat-grid, .cta-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .motto-main { font-size: 1.15rem; }

      .timeline {
        display: block; min-height: 0; margin: 2.6rem 0;
        width: 100%; padding: 0; transform: none;
      }
      .tl-body,
      .timeline li:nth-child(even) .tl-body {
        position: static; width: auto; transform: none;
        top: auto; bottom: auto;
      }
      .timeline::before {
        left: 5px; right: auto; top: 0.5rem; bottom: 0.5rem;
        width: 2px; height: auto; transform: none;
        background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(44,95,87,0.22), var(--primary));
      }
      .timeline li,
      .timeline li:nth-child(even) {
        display: block; height: auto; text-align: left;
        padding: 0 0 0 1.9rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      }
      .timeline li:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
      .timeline li::before,
      .timeline li:nth-child(even)::before {
        left: -1px; top: 0.45rem; transform: none;
      }
      .timeline li::after,
      .timeline li:nth-child(even)::after { display: none; }
      .tl-title { font-size: 1rem; white-space: normal; }
      .tl-desc { font-size: 0.88rem; white-space: normal; }
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
